<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10012549>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Ventral habitus of Prothyma (Symplecthyma). a) P. inopinata sp. nov.; b) P. kapuka sp. nov.; c) P. aeneoparva Horn, 1934. Scale = 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10012549/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10012553>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Prothyma (Symplecthyma) aeneoparva Horn, 1934. a–f: Dorsal habitus. Scale = 5 mm. a) Female, Leyte. b) P. nitida Rivalier 1964 syn. nov., Type, male. c) P. boholensis Dheurle 2012 syn. nov., Holotype, female. d) Male from Cawa- Cawa, Mindanao. e) Male, Park Tayabas, Luzon. f) Lectotype, male, Samar. g) Labrum, Male. h) Labrum, Female. Scale = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10012553/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10012559>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Aedeagus of Prothyma (Symplecthyma) aeneoparva Horn, 1934, left lateral view. a) Syntype, Biliran; b) Lope DeVega, Samar, lateral and ventral view; c) Syntype, Samar; d) Hinabangan, Samar; e) P. nitida Rivalier 1964 syn. nov., Type, drawing from (Rivalier, 1964); f) Segod, Leyte; g) Park Tayabas, Luzon; h) Surigao, Mindanao; i) Wao, Mindanao; j) Sibagat; k) Cawa-Cawa, Mindanao; l) Gutalac, Mindanao; m) Cabanglasan, Mindanao; n) Esperanza, Mindanao. Scale = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10012559/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10012595>
    dc:description "FIGURE 14. Head and pronotum of Symplecthyma species. a–c: Prothyma (Symplecthyma) aeneoparva Horn, 1934; a) Lectotype, Samar; b) Cawa-Cawa, Mindanao; c) Park Tayabas, Luzon; d) Prothyma (Symplecthyma) eureka sp. nov., Paratype. e) Prothyma (Symplecthyma) heteromallicollis Horn, 1909, Holotype. f) Prothyma (Symplecthyma) sciakyi sp. nov., Holotype. Scale = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10012595/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

